queries.sql: SELECT u.id as id_alumno, u.matricula, CONCAT(IFNULL(u.ap_Alumno,''), ' ', IFNULL(u.am_Alumno,''), ' ', u.Nombre) as nombre_completo, c.Id_cal, c.id_materia, c.calificacion, c.faltas, c.bandera FROM usr u LEFT JOIN calificacion c ON u.id = c.id_usr AND c.id_grado = '28' AND c.cicloEscolar = '11' AND c.id_mes = '4' WHERE u.grado = '28' AND u.estatus = 1 AND u.nivel = 7 ORDER BY u.ap_Alumno, u.am_Alumno, u.Nombre

timelineData.query: SELECT u.id as id_alumno, u.matricula, CONCAT(IFNULL(u.ap_Alumno,''), ' ', IFNULL(u.am_Alumno,''), ' ', u.Nombre) as nombre_completo, c.Id_cal, c.id_materia, c.calificacion, c.faltas, c.bandera FROM usr u LEFT JOIN calificacion c ON u.id = c.id_usr AND c.id_grado = '28' AND c.cicloEscolar = '11' AND c.id_mes = '4' WHERE u.grado = '28' AND u.estatus = 1 AND u.nivel = 7 ORDER BY u.ap_Alumno, u.am_Alumno, u.Nombre
